  "description": "SOLVE=0.5 with targetWarmth=0.7 and targetSpace=0.8 steers OUTWIT toward warm, spacious character — reducing brightness, increasing den mix. OUTWIT CA amplitude opens OceanDeep's Darkness Filter Ceiling via AmpToFilter: trigger density momentarily lifts the 50-800 Hz ceiling, allowing brief high-frequency transients to emerge from the pressure zone. OceanDeep's envelope drives OUTWIT chromatophore via EnvToMorph — the bioluminescent exciter's light pulses color the octopus. Discrete CA triggers become raw material for deep-pressure synthesis.",
